Invocation Name: autocompare
des: Autocompare by Skillset.ai helps you makes smarter decisions while saving time. When you want to make a decision between two things searching the web, reading reviews or watching videos takes so much time. With the autocompare skill on Alexa you can automatically compare foods to each other to make the smarter choice. We've also just added the ability to compare one movie to another. The system gathers tons of data and makes sense of it to help you make the smarter choice.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
